ter value to \'1\'.\r\n\r\nIn case you are intend to use PayPal IPN, you will need to specify your business email address for \'business\' parameter.' , 'credit_card_info.php' , NULL , NULL , NULL , NULL , NULL , 'GET' , 0 , 1 , 'https://api-aa.paypal.com/2.0/' , './payments/paypal_direct.php' , NULL , NULL , NULL , 4 , 6 , 10 , 1 , 0 , 0 , 0 , 1 , 1 , NULL , NULL , NULL , NULL , 0 , NULL , NULL , NULL , NULL ) ;
