his customer after a set amount of time? Must be \'1\' if TrialFlag is \'1\', otherwise optional\r\n\r\nRebillAmount - Amount in USD of the automatic rebill. Mandatory if Rebill is \'1\', otherwise ignored.\r\nRebillDateType - \r\n\'d\' (day), \'m\' (month), \'y\' (year) The units expressed in RebillDateValue.Mandatory if Rebill is \'1\' otherwise ignored.\r\n\r\nRebillDateValue - Number of units specified in RebillDateType to wait between automatic rebilling. Mandatory if Rebill is \'1\' otherwise ignored.\r\n\r\nUserExpire - (7/7/2004 12:29:02 PM) When should this users access expire?\r\nMust be valid date format. Mandatory if AddUser=1 and Rebill=0\r\n\r\nTEST - \'TRUE\' or \'FALSE\' Optional' , 'credit_card_info.php' , NULL , NULL , NULL , NULL , NULL , 'GET' , 0 , 1 , 'https://secure.2000charge.com/Secure/MasterRemoteProcess.asp' , './payments/dgl_eudebit.php' , NULL , NULL , NULL , 4 , 6 , 10 , 1 , 0 , 0 , 0 , 1 , 1 , NULL , NULL , NULL , NULL , NULL , NULL , NULL , NULL , NULL ) ;
