sed in a popup screen or in a frameset/iframe.\r\n- FRAME = pages in iframe/frame\r\n- POPUP = pages in popup screen\r\nBPE_Autoclose_Popup - (Optional) You have to set in this field if the screen needs to be closed automatic when you use a popup screen. The popup will be closed directly when loading the response. Your own return page informs the customer about the results of the transaction. The possible values are:\r\n- 1, ja, yes, true = JA\r\n- 0, nee, no, false = NEE\r\n\r\nFor Buckaroo action_url:\r\nhttps://payment.buckaroo.nl/sslplus/request_for_authorization.asp\r\n\r\nFor iDeal action_url:\r\nhttps://payment.buckaroo.nl/gateway/ideal_payment.asp\r\nBPE_Currency and Currency always - EUR = Euro' , './payments/buckaroo_ssl_process.php' , NULL , NULL , NULL , NULL , NULL , 'GET' , NULL , 0 , NULL , NULL , NULL , NULL , NULL , NULL , NULL , NULL , NULL , 0 , 0 , 0 , 1 , 1 , NULL , NULL , NULL , NULL , 0 , NULL , NULL , NULL , NULL ) ;
